data.name: hoverButton3.Text
data.value:
This API serves three main types of users: Employees can manage their profiles, view attendance, request leave, and access payroll details. Managers can approve or reject leave requests and access performance reviews of their team members. HR Administrators have full access to employee data, including payroll, attendance, and performance reviews.
With easy-to-use endpoints for key HR operations, this system simplifies HR tasks, improves efficiency, and ensures seamless communication between employees, managers, and HR staff

data.name: hoverButton2.Text
data.value: The WorkForce HR API is a backend system designed to streamline and automate Human Resource (HR) operations within an organization. It offers essential tools to manage employee records, track attendance, process payroll, handle leave requests, and store performance reviews.
